The following versions of the TinyMCE library were excluded from minification to resolve issues
that occurred when JavaScript minification was enabled in production mode.

Enabling minification caused TinyMCE versions 6 and 7 to generate errors in the browser console,
impacting functionality and the user experience.

This issue has been resolved in Adobe Commerce 2.4.8.

